---
const title = "Lightbox Example";
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <p>
    Here's two examples using popular lightbox libraries (<a
      href="https://lokeshdhakar.com/projects/lightbox2/">Lightbox 2</a
    > and <a href="https://photoswipe.com/">PhotoSwipe</a>).
